query:
UPDATE users SET username = CASE 
  WHEN id = 1 THEN 'ahmedjassim1234'
  WHEN id = 2 THEN 'testuser5678'
  WHEN id = 3 THEN 'demouser9012'
  ELSE CONCAT('user', id, FLOOR(RAND() * 1000))
END WHERE username IS NULL OR username = ''
